gText_Birch_Welcome::
	.string "Haere mai, e hoa. Welcome.\p"
	.string "You kept me waiting…\n"
	.string "but I am a patient man.\l"
	.string "I once slowed the sun itself.\p"
	.string "This is Aotearoa…\n"
	.string "the land of the long white cloud.\p"
	.string "And the land of Pokémon.\p"
	.string "$"

gText_Birch_Pokemon::
	.string "This one? Solrock.\n"
	.string "We go way back.\p"
	.string "Long ago, I snared the sun itself…\n"
	.string "made it walk slower across the\l"
	.string "sky, so people had time to live.\p"
	.string "…It still pinches an hour back\n"
	.string "off me every spring, mind you.\l"
	.string "We have an arrangement.\p"
	.string "$"

gText_Birch_MainSpeech::
	.string "Long ago, this land was fished up\n"
	.string "out of the sea…\p"
	.string "and every living thing here…\n"
	.string "bird and taniwha, person and\l"
	.string "Pokémon… has a place in its story.\p"
	.string "People and Pokémon live side by\n"
	.string "side in Aotearoa… as friends,\l"
	.string "as workmates, as family.\p"
	.string "Some climb mountains together.\n"
	.string "Some cross the sea.\p"
	.string "And some are sent far from home…\n"
	.string "to find out who they really are.\p"
	.string "$"

gText_Birch_AndYouAre::
	.string "And you, e hoa…\n"
	.string "who are you?$"

gText_Birch_BoyOrGirl::
	.string "Are you a boy?\n"
	.string "Or are you a girl?$"

gText_Birch_WhatsYourName::
	.string "Tell me your name.$"

gText_Birch_SoItsPlayer::
	.string "So it's {PLAYER}{KUN}?$"

gText_Birch_YourePlayer::
	.string "{PLAYER}, of Heretaunga.\p"
	.string "Born in the curve of the Bay…\n"
	.string "where the hook first caught\l"
	.string "the land.\p"
	.string "I know your family well.\n"
	.string "…Better than you might guess.\p"
	.string "$"

gText_Birch_AreYouReady::
	.string "It's your birthday today,\n"
	.string "isn't it?\p"
	.string "Your whole family is gathering\n"
	.string "at the orchard. All of them.\l"
	.string "That doesn't happen often.\p"
	.string "Take courage, e hoa.\p"
	.string "Climb high… but keep your feet\n"
	.string "on the earth that grew you.\p"
	.string "We will meet again.\p"
	.string "$"
